    {
      "review_id": "rJggAvorhQ",
      "rebuttal_id": "rJgfByXdRQ",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "text": "3. To avoid confusion of the proposed method to utilize techniques of DGR[3] in order to prevent forgetting in the G, we kindly ask the reviewer to refer to our response (2) to the Reviewer 1.",
