    {
      "review_id": "rJggAvorhQ",
      "rebuttal_id": "rJgfByXdRQ",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "text": "Concerning the time comparison, there is no reason why our approach should be less time efficient then DGR based approaches [1, 3] as our method does not require retraining the generator from scratch at each time step.",
